abstract: New York Jets guard Brandon Moore responds to Santonio Holmes' critical comments about the offensive line, saying teammates should keep such remarks to themselves.
snippet: Responding to remarks by Santonio Holmes, the Jets’ Brandon Moore said teammates should keep such comments to themselves.
lead_paragraph: Responding to remarks by Santonio Holmes, the Jets’ Brandon Moore said teammates should keep such comments to themselves.

headline.main: Jets Guard Says Internal Critics Hurt Team Unity
